ly internal, now released as a standalone service\n- **Special optimization**: Particularly optimized for **Claude Code** and **Cursor**\n- **One-command deployment**: Deploy full-stack applications with a single command\n- **No backend setup**: Eliminates the hassle of backend configuration and setup\n\n### **Performance on Product Hunt**\n- **Upvotes**: 462 upvotes\n- **Featured status**: Listed on the daily leaderboard\n\n### **Website**\n- **Official site**: base44.com\n\n---\n\n## Additional Context About Base44\n\nFrom the search results, I also found broader information about Base44:\n\n### **Company Background**\n- Founded by Israeli entrepreneur **Maor Shlomo**\n- **Acquired by Wix** in June 2025 for **$80 million** (after just 6 months of operation)\n- Team of only 9 people, was already profitable with $189K monthly profit\n- Over **300,000 users** at time of acquisition\n\n### **Core Product Evolution**\nBase44 has evolved through several iterations:\n- **Base44 2.0** (March 2025): Comprehensive no-code application building platform\n- **Base44: The all-new builder** (October 2025): More intelligent, faster, and intuitive app creation\n- **Base44 Backend Platform** (February 2026): Focused backend services for AI applications\n\n### **Core Value Proposition**\nBase44 positions itself as an \"AI application factory for non-technical and product teams,\" allowing users to generate complete applications with login systems, databases, and permission frameworks through text descriptions alone—essentially providing a \"24/7 full-stack team\" experience.\n\nThe February 2026 Product Hunt launch specifically targeted developers building AI-powered applications, with special emphasis on integration with Claude Code and Cursor development environments.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
