        "content": "Web search results for query: \"\"Inspector\" Figma Claude Code February 2026\"\n\nI'll perform a web search for that query.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"社区云\",\"url\":\"https://devpress.csdn.net/tags/63f861b3986c660f3cf909e1\"},{\"title\":\"Figma 联手 Anthropic，推出 AI 代码转设计工具\",\"url\":\"https://accesspath.com/product/figma-launches-tool-to-convert-mlr9ysj2cm4l\"},{\"title\":\"Product Hunt 每日热榜 | 2026-02-09\",\"url\":\"https://m.toutiao.com/a7606695561483321897/\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code 配置Figma MCP 实战指南 - 稀土掘金\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7594396779022925887\"},{\"title\":\"我从X和Reddit扒了这12 个高级玩法,把 Claude Code 变成可交付系统\",\"url\":\"https://mparticle.uc.cn/article_org.html?uc_param_str=frdnsnpfvecpntnwprdssskt#!wm_cid=702200123689537536!!wm_id=115df2adc88243b4a2e4e12a55b48244\"},{\"title\":\"MatthewDailey/figma-mcp: ModelContextProtocol for ... - GitHub\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/MatthewDailey/figma-mcp\"},{\"title\":\"爆款AI产品Pencil的新模式！如何将Claude Code制作成桌面应用？\",\"url\":\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1855354338105135386\"},{\"title\":\"AI开发：claude+Figma+VS CODE 从UI到页面\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7573892156256862244\"},{\"title\":\"Claude Code全局添加figma MCP\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7573508361740877824\"},{\"title\":\"Claude + Figma MCP 实战教程- 日记- 豆瓣\",\"url\":\"https://m.douban.com/note/875445917/\"}]\n\nBased on my web search, here's what I found about \"Inspector,\" Figma, Claude Code, and their relationship in February 2026:\n\n## Key Findings\n\n### **Inspector - New Visual Editor Tool**\nInspector is a **visual editor tool** designed to connect with popular AI agents like **Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor**. It was featured on Product Hunt around February 9, 2026, with the tagline \"Figma for Claude Code.\" The tool allows users to edit front-end interfaces using a Figma-like approach and received significant attention (462+ votes).\n\n### **Figma & Anthropic Partnership - \"Code to Canvas\"**\nAround February 17, 2026, **Figma officially partnered with Anthropic** (Claude's developer) to launch a feature called **\"Code to Canvas\"**. This integration allows users to:\n- Transfer AI-generated code from Claude Code directly to Figma's design environment\n- Automatically convert browser render states into fully editable Figma layers\n- Simply type \"Send this to Figma\" in Claude Code to initiate the transfer\n\n### **Figma MCP (Model Context Protocol) Integration**\nThere's extensive documentation about integrating Figma with Claude Code using MCP:\n- **Official Figma MCP**: Available at `https://mcp.figma.com/mcp` for Claude Code users\n- Requires Figma Dev or Full seat (professional/enterprise account) to enable Dev Mode MCP Server\n- Supports both desktop and command-line interfaces\n- **Free tier limitation**: Only 6 uses per month for free users\n\n### **Key Features Available**\n1. **Selection-based code generation**: Generate code from selected Figma frames\n2. **Link-based conversion**: Convert designs via Figma links\n3. **Multiple output formats**: React, Vue, Tailwind, HTML/CSS/JS\n4. **Design system integration**: Extract variables, components, and design tokens\n5. **Visual consistency**: Maintain pixel-perfect accuracy (around 80% restoration rate)\n\n### **Industry Context**\nThis development occurred during what traders called the \"SaaS apocalypse\" in early 2026, where software stocks lost nearly $1 trillion in market value. Figma launched this feature just before their Q4 2026 earnings release.\n\nThe integration represents a growing trend of making Claude Code the foundational AI agent for various productivity tools, eliminating the need for separate AI subscriptions across different applications.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
