ack deployment and no backend setup required.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-17\",\n    \"category\": \"AI backend platform\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"462 upvotes on Product Hunt\",\n      \"AI agents use simple skills instead of complex APIs\",\n      \"Deploy full-stack applications with npx base44@latest create\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Happycapy\",\n    \"url\": \"https://happycapy.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Browser-based cloud computer pre-loaded with Claude Code and other AI models. Provides 2 vCPU / 4GB RAM / 10GB SSD sandbox environment with no local installation required. Works on both desktop and mobile.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-23\",\n    \"category\": \"Cloud-based AI IDE\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"Topped Product Hunt weekly chart with 948 upvotes\",\n      \"Zero-barrier cloud-based agent workstation\",\n      \"No Docker setup or local installation needed\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Mastra Code\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/mastra-code\",\n    \"description\": \"AI programming agent featuring observational memory and support for long-term coding sessions. Provides precise context management, rapid application building, and data compression for extended development work.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-27\",\n    \"category\": \"AI code agent\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"204 upvotes on Product Hunt and featured\",\n      \"Focus on maintaining context across long coding sessions\",\n      \"Observational memory enhances development workflow\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Inspector\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/inspector\",\n    \"description\": \"Visual editor tool described as 'Figma for Claude Code' that connects with AI agents like Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor. Allows editing front-end interfaces using a Figma-like approach and applying changes through AI agents.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-14\",\n    \"category\": \"Visual AI code editor\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"462 upvotes on Product Hunt\",\n      \"Figma-like interface for editing production websites\",\n      \"Bridge between design tools and AI coding agents\"\n    ]\n  }\n]",
  "new_string": "[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Happycapy\",\n    \"url\": \"https://happycapy.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Browser-based cloud computer pre-loaded with Claude Code and other AI models. Provides 2 vCPU / 4GB RAM / 10GB SSD sandbox environment with no local installation required. Works on both desktop and mobile devices as an 'Agent-Native Computer for ordinary people'.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-23\",\n    \"category\": \"Cloud-based AI IDE\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"Topped Product Hunt weekly chart with 948 upvotes\",\n      \"Zero-barrier cloud-based agent workstation\",\n      \"No Docker setup or local installation needed\",\n      \"Web-based and mobile-friendly alternative to OpenClaw\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Mastra Code\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/mastra-code\",\n    \"description\": \"AI programming agent featuring observational memory and support for long-term coding sessions. Provides precise context management, rapid application building, and data compression for extended development work with workspace memory capabilities.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-27\",\n    \"category\": \"AI code agent with workspace memory\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"204 upvotes on Product Hunt and featured\",\n      \"Focus on maintaining context across long coding sessions\",\n      \"Observational memory enhances development workflow\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Superset\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/superset\",\n    \"description\": \"AI IDE that runs multiple coding assistants (Claude Code, Codex, etc.) simultaneously with independent sandboxing, unified monitoring, built-in diff viewer, and real-time notifications. Designed to reduce context switching and improve development efficiency by up to 10x.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-27\",\n    \"category\": \"Multi-agent AI IDE\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"478 upvotes on Product Hunt and featured\",\n      \"Run multiple AI coding assistants simultaneously\",\n      \"Independent sandboxing prevents agent interference\",\n      \"Unified monitoring across all assistants\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Agent Bar\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/agent-bar\",\n    \"description\": \"Native macOS menu bar application that provides a GUI for Claude Code. Features include project selection, voice interaction, real-time tool call monitoring, action approval/auto-approval, and cost tracking - all without leaving the desktop.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-16\",\n    \"category\": \"AI coding CLI tool\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"139 upvotes on Product Hunt and featured\",\n      \"Run Claude Code directly from your menu bar\",\n      \"Native GUI makes terminal-based Claude Code more accessible\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Base44 Backend Platform\",\n    \"url\": \"https://base44.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Complete backend service specifically designed for building AI agent applications. Previously internal tool tested on millions of applications, now released as standalone service. Optimized for Claude Code and Cursor with one-command full-stack deployment via 'npx base44@latest create'.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-17\",\n    \"category\": \"AI backend platform for agents\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"462 upvotes on Product Hunt\",\n      \"AI agents use simple skills instead of complex APIs\",\n      \"No backend setup or configuration required\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Cline CLI 2.0\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/cline-cli\",\n    \"description\": \"Command-line tool bringing autonomous coding with parallel agents and headless CI/CD capabilities. Fully open source with redesigned architecture, MCP support, and trusted by over 5 million developers. Integrates with Qwen, Claude, Gemini, and DeepSeek models.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-15\",\n    \"category\": \"AI coding CLI\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"255 upvotes on Product Hunt and featured\",\n      \"Parallel agents support for autonomous coding\",\n      \"Headless CI/CD integration in terminal\"\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Inspector\",\n    \"url\": \"https://producthunt.com/posts/inspector\",\n    \"description\": \"Visual editor tool described as 'Figma for Claude Code' that connects with AI agents like Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor. Allows editing front-end interfaces using a Figma-like approach and applying changes through AI agents to production websites.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-02-14\",\n    \"category\": \"Visual AI code editor\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\n      \"462 upvotes on Product Hunt\",\n      \"Figma-like interface for editing production websites\",\n      \"Bridge between design tools and AI coding agents\"\n    ]\n  }\n]"
